Package jakarta.nosql.mapping.document

Interface DocumentEventPersistManager

  • public interface DocumentEventPersistManager
    This interface represents the manager of events. When an entity be either saved or updated an event will be fired. This order gonna be: 1) firePreEntity 2) firePreDocumentEntity 3) firePreDocument 4) firePostDocument 5) firePostEntity 6) firePostDocumentEntity
    See Also:
    DocumentWorkflow
